Heel!

606
00:54:35,147 --> 00:54:38,317
That means nothing
to you I suppose.

607
00:54:39,902 --> 00:54:42,780
What's the third thing?

608
00:54:42,863 --> 00:54:43,906
What do you mean?

609
00:54:43,989 --> 00:54:45,324
All living things.

610
00:54:45,407 --> 00:54:48,994
They find food,
protect their young,

611
00:54:49,077 --> 00:54:50,579
What's the third
thing they do?

