767
01:10:50,872 --> 01:10:51,831
Not funny.

768
01:10:56,252 --> 01:10:58,004
Look, they'll be here soon.

769
01:10:59,922 --> 01:11:01,591
Yeah, well, not soon enough.

770
01:11:03,092 --> 01:11:04,385
