924
01:24:38,323 --> 01:24:41,285
You got your shark.

925
01:24:41,368 --> 01:24:42,619
Yeah, yeah, yeah.

926
01:24:42,703 --> 01:24:46,164
Not a bad night. We cleaned
up the lake and the street.

